OL,5, A man who bludgeoned a retired lawyer  
OL,6, to death with a hammer "would have     
OL,7, killed again", a court has heard.      
OL,9,FDavid Iwo, 24, murdered Martin Decker  
OL,10,Fat the 69-year-old's home on Vyner     
OL,11,FCroft, Birkenhead, on 6 March.         
OL,13,FAlan Kent QC, prosecuting, said it was 
OL,14,Fpart of a campaign of violent robberies
OL,15,Fagainst vulnerable men and Iwo "would  
OL,16,Fnot have stopped until he was caught". 
OL,18,FIwo, of Liverpool, laughed as he was   
OL,19,Fjailed for a minimum of 33 years at    
OL,20,FPreston Crown Court.                   
